130
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:29,340
He only said

131
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,220
he's from Sen'an Pharma.

132
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:34,100
He promised my dad could continue the trial.

133
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,980
That's why I agreed to say that.

134
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,810
So who should feel guilty?

135
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:44,850
We saw the risks,

136
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:46,050
yet plan to ignore them.

137
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,580
Shouldn't we feel ashamed?

138
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,810
There are over 10 million Alzheimer's patients

139
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,100
in our country.

140
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,810
Even if the serious adverse reaction rate

141
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:55,810
is only 1%,

142
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:57,170
