145
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,050
Or to save people?

146
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:05,930
Isn't the original intention

147
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:07,780
of making drugs

148
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,700
to ensure everyone's health

149
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,490
and safety?

150
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,980
You say I have personal emotions,

151
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:17,780
I admit it.

152
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,700
Because I'm in PV.

153
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,580
It's my duty,

154
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:24,170
and my conscience.

155
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,810
Therefore, I advocate

156
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,660
for extending

157
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,050
the phase Ⅲ trial of SA-0988

158
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,780
to further test its safety.

159
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,540
And this case of SUSAR

160
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,540
must be reported to the authorities!

161
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,580
Today, our PV Dept

162
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,780
