249
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,770
Don't worry about it.

250
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,220
Let's eat.

251
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,300
Let's eat.

252
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:08,940
Jiaqi!

253
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,490
Mom!

254
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,580
