00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:46,860
Hey?

588
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,490
Jiaqi, come out for a drink.

589
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,170
Alright.

590
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,490
Jialu is asking me out.

591
00:35:15,220 --> 00:35:18,300
♪They all keep asking how I'm supposed to heal♪

592
00:35:20,260 --> 00:35:24,460
♪But what's the point of questioning what's already gone...♪

593
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:26,680
We're leaving!

594
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:27,340
You're off tomorrow?

595
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:27,800
[Galaxy Tavern]

596
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:28,490
See you!

597
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,340
Bye!

598
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:32,900
If all else fails,

599
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,170
just let my sister

600
00:35:34,230 --> 00:35:35,210
teach you square dancing.

601
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,490
That'll definitely

602
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,260
leave foreigners stunned.

603
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,530
You think square dancing is easy to learn?

604
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:40,690
We silly old men

605
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:42,130
can't even outdance those old ladies.

606
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,210
We'll be laughed at

607
00:35:43,230 --> 00:35:44,380
by An's classmates.

608
00:35:46,380 --> 00:35:49,020
♪Is a symphony called betrayal♪

609
00:35:56,060 --> 00:35:58,260
♪Your silent response♪

610
00:35:59,020 --> 00:36:04,180
♪Sends me into the abyss of confusion♪

611
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:07,140
♪Me and myself♪

612
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:10,140
♪This restless side of me♪

613
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:16,260
♪Dancing through the night, trying to soothe a heart torn apart♪

614
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:19,420
♪I look at myself♪

615
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:22,460
♪The marks of being deceived♪

616
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:28,620
♪Trying to open my heart, but always stepping on shattered glass♪

617
00:36:29,380 --> 00:36:32,180
♪If promises can't be escaped♪

618
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:38,340
♪If true hearts can't be abandoned♪

619
00:36:40,380 --> 00:36:44,260
♪All that's left is me, healing myself♪

620
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:04,820
[Loving Strangers]

621
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,010
Let me go!

622
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:08,210
I've already seen through you!

623
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,420
You're nothing but a coward,

624
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,300
always hesitating,

625
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,980
hiding behind kindness like a shield.

626
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:13,980
Jiang Jiaqi,

627
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:15,490
are you scared?

628
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,690
Are you willing to just walk away like this?

629
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,980
Can we

630
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,460
not see each other for a while?

631
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:22,690
Treat me to a meal.

632
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,820
We came into this world

633
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,380
just to be punished.

634
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:30,090
Want me to take him out for you?

635
00:37:47,580 --> 00:37:50,980
♪A light hiding in the dark♪

636
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:54,540
♪Reflects my panic inside♪

637
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:59,620
♪Locked for so long in a narrow crack♪

638
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:05,060
♪Life chasing us into surrender♪

639
00:38:05,740 --> 00:38:09,060
♪We're all the same♪

640
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:13,380
♪Burdened with a load that steals our breath♪

641
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:19,740
♪Unwilling to live so ordinary♪

642
00:38:20,380 --> 00:38:23,620
♪But how do we even cry out♪

643
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:27,500
♪Our helplessness to the sky?♪

644
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:31,900
♪When dandelions drift far away♪

645
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:35,460
♪Lone buds fly against the wind♪

646
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:39,060
♪Fleeing into a boundless haze♪

647
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:42,620
♪Burying yesterday♪

648
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:46,300
♪When dandelions drift far away♪

649
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:49,860
♪Lone buds fly against the wind♪

650
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:53,460
♪Fleeing into a boundless haze♪

651
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:56,780
♪Burying yesterday♪

652
00:38:57,260 --> 00:39:00,340
♪When dandelions sail far away♪

653
00:39:00,740 --> 00:39:03,820
♪Pushing me back to my first dream♪

654
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:06,500
♪Even covered in scars♪

655
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:10,060
♪I still press on♪
